                <div class="tip-box">
                    <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Prefixes change the meaning of words. "Un-" reverses meaning (happy ‚Üí unhappy), "pre-" means before (historic ‚Üí prehistoric).
                </div>
                <div id="prefixes-list"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- SUFFIXES TAB -->
        <div id="suffixes-content" class="tab-content">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Suffixes change word type. "-tion" makes verbs into nouns (create ‚Üí creation), "-ful" makes adjectives (beauty ‚Üí beautiful).
                </div>
                <div id="suffixes-list"></div>
            </div>
